title: Dj Mujava - Township Funk - Vinyl  + Many Remixes
description:
This is my collection of remixes and original production tracks for "Township Funk" by DJ Mujava.

This is, to my knowlege every internet remix of the track, and all of the vinyl that the track or its remixes were on, including whitelabel promo vinyl.


Enjoy!
